    "html": "<h1>The basics of<span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">SER</span><span>&nbsp;</span>and<span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(196, 99, 116);\">ESTAR</span></h1>\r\n<h2 jscontroller=\"Ae65rd\" jsaction=\"touchstart:UrsOsc; click:KjsqPd; focusout:QZoaZ; mouseover:y0pDld; mouseout:dq0hvd;fv1Rjc:jbFSOd;CrfLRd:SzACGe;\" class=\"CjVfdc\"><span class=\"C9DxTc \">What is the basic meaning of<span>&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"C9DxTc \" style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">SER</span><span class=\"C9DxTc \"><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">&nbsp;</span>&amp;<span>&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"C9DxTc \" style=\"color: rgb(196, 99, 116);\">ESTAR</span><span class=\"C9DxTc \">?</span></h2>\r\n<p><span class=\"C9DxTc \"><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\"><strong>SER</strong>&nbsp;</span>expresses&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">the essence</span>&nbsp;</strong>of someone or something. Think of&nbsp;<strong>e</strong><strong>ssence</strong><span>&nbsp;</span>as any quality or attribute that<span>&nbsp;</span><strong>defines</strong>&nbsp;<em>how&nbsp;</em>someone or something is perceived. This is what&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\"><strong>SER</strong></span><span>&nbsp;</span>is at its core.</span></p>\r\n<details class=\"pp-accordion\" open=\"\">\r\n<summary><strong><span>💬Common examples that describe </span><em>essence </em><span>with </span><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">SER</span></strong></summary>\r\n<div class=\"pp-accordion-body\">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Identity</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Juan y Carla<span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">son</span><span>&nbsp;</span>mis mejores amigos.</strong><span><br></span><em>Juan and Carla are my best friends.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<