"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es&nbsp;</span></span>muy suave.</strong><span><br></span><em>Her/His voice is very soft.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Profession</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Mi pap&aacute;<span> <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es&nbsp;</span></span>m&eacute;dico.</strong><span><br></span><em>My dad is a doctor.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Ellos<span> <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">son</span> </span>profesores de historia.</strong><span><br></span><em>They are history teachers.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Personal Relationships</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Carolina<span> <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es&nbsp;</span></span>mi prima.</strong><span><br></span><em>Carolina is my cousin.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Nosotros <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">somos</span><span>&nbsp;</span>novios.</strong><span><br></span><em>We're a couple (boyfriend &amp; girlfriend/boyfriends)</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Category</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Los gatos<span> <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">son</span> </span>mam&iacute;feros.</strong><span><br></span><em>Cats are mammals.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Este libro<span> <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es&nbsp;</span></span>una novela de ciencia ficci&oacute;n.</strong><span><br></span><em>This book is a science fiction novel.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Shape</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>La mesa<span> <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es&nbsp;</span></span>redonda.</strong><span><br></span><em>The table is round.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Mis gafas<span> <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">son</span> </span>rectangulares.</strong><span><br></span><em>My glasses are rectangular.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Dates</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Hoy<span> <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es&nbsp;</span></span>martes.</strong><span><br></span><em>Today is Tuesday.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Mi cumplea&ntilde;os<span> <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es&nbsp;</span></span>el 10 de abril.</strong><span><br></span><em>My birthday is on April 10th.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Times</strong></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong>Ahora<span> <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es&nbsp;</span></span>la una y media de la tarde.</strong><span><br></span><em>Right now, it is 1:30 in the afternoon.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">son</span><span>&nbsp;</span>las 17 horas. /&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">son</span><span>&nbsp;</span>las cinco de la tarde.</strong><span><br></span><em>It's 5:00 pm.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"2\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\"><span></span><strong>La reuni&oacute;n<span> <span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\">es&nbsp;</span></span>a las cinco.</strong><span><br></span><em>The meeting is at five.</em></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</details>\r\n<p><span class=\"C9DxTc \"><span style=\"color: rgb(196, 99, 116);\"><strong>ESTAR</strong>&nbsp;</span>expresses&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(196, 99, 116);\">the situation</span>&nbsp;</strong>of someone or something. This is&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(196, 99, 116);\"><strong>ESTAR&nbsp;</strong></span>at its core.</span></p>\r\n<details class=\"pp-accordion\" open=\"\">\r\n<summary><strong><span>⚠️Problems with traditional explanations</span></strong></summary>\r\n<div class=\"pp-accordion-body\">\r\n<p><span class=\"C9DxTc \">You may have seen or heard explanations like \"<em>SER</em><em><span>&nbsp;</span>is used with permanent characteristics and ESTAR with temporary ones.\"</em><span>&nbsp;</span>This usually holds up, but also causes confusion when you run into examples like these:</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong><span class=\"C9DxTc \">El Everest<span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(196, 99, 116);\">est&aacute;&nbsp;</span>en el sur de Asia, cerca de</span></strong><span class=\"C9DxTc \"><span>&nbsp;</span><strong>Nepal.</strong><em><br></em><em>Mt. Everest is in Southern Asia, near Nepal.</em></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span class=\"C9DxTc \">The location of Mount Everest seems like a permanent feature &mdash; barring a devastating asteroid impact, war, or some other catastrophe &mdash; so why did we use&nbsp;ESTAR&nbsp;instead of&nbsp;SER? Further on in this guide, you'll see why we think of the location of places as&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(196, 99, 116);\"><strong>situational</strong>&nbsp;</span>instead of as&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(143, 142, 197);\"><strong>essential</strong></span>.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</details>\r\n<h3><span class=\"C9DxTc \">[placeholder]</span></h3>\r\n<div style=\"position: relative; width: 100%; height: 0; padding-top: 56.2500%; padding-bottom: 0; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px 0 rgba(63,69,81,0.16); margin-top: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 0.9em; overflow: hidden; border-radius: 8px; will-change: transform;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.canva.com/design/DAGOfM70F9E/BQDirBfUXRbjR88Eh4Et3A/view?embed\" allow=\"fullscreen\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" width=\"\" height=\"\" style=\"position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; top: 0; left: 0; border: none; padding: 0; margin: 0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\r\n  </iframe></div>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"C9DxTc \"></span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"C9DxTc \"></span></p>",
